{
  "chapter": 96,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十六回：奸狡诡诈\n\n本章讲述了江玉郎在移花宫主离开后，与铁萍姑的对话，以及十大恶人（李大嘴、屠娇娇、哈哈儿、白开心）的出现。十大恶人看中了江玉郎的奸诈性格，邀请他加入组织替代已死的欧阳兄弟。他们要求江玉郎潜入魏无牙的山洞，寻找几只用仇人血调成油漆的黑色铁箱子。江玉郎贪财好色，接受了任务，抛下铁萍姑前往魏无牙处。本章展现了江玉郎的虚伪与十大恶人的阴谋，为后续剧情埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "宫主，求求宫主饶了他吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你为他求情，又有谁为你求情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "婢子自知罪孽深重，本就不敢求宫主饶恕的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "很好，那么我问你，你将小鱼儿带到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "小鱼儿他……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "小鱼儿他怎么样了？你为何不说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "他……他也到了这里，只怕是在东面那一带。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "好，我这就去找他，但愿你说的不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "够了，停手吧。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "多…多谢宫主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在，我要你在这里看着她，若有人伤了她，我就要你的命，若有人将她救走，我也要你的命，知道么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "小人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是移花宫主，原来移花宫主就是这样子的，想不到我今日竟见着了她，只怕是走了运了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "幸好今日来的只是小宫主，若是大宫主来了，你我此刻只怕都活不成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但等她回来，你我还是活不成的，你害了小鱼儿，她绝不会饶你。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "为什么？她本来不是要花无缺杀小鱼儿的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，但她只许花无缺自己亲手杀小鱼儿，却不许别人动小鱼儿一根手指，就连她自己，也绝不伤小鱼儿的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这又是为了什么？倒真是件怪事！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我也猜不透这是什么道理，她们姐妹本来就是个怪人，无论如何，你现在快将我放下去吧，我半身发麻，已被她点了穴道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我就算救了你，咱们俩人还是逃不脱她掌握的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但咱们好歹也得试一试，等她回来了，反正也只有一死，现在若是逃走，找个地方藏起来，说不定还可过几天快活的日子。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但你若不告诉她小鱼儿是被我害死的，她也就不会杀我了，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "也许……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你方才既已骗过了她，为什么不再骗下去呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但……但我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你既然反正是要死的，为何要我陪你一起死呢？你若真的对我好，就该牺牲自己来救我，我一定永远也忘不了你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极，我已有很久没听过这么妙的话了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位仁兄若是女的，萧咪咪见着他一定要自愧不如。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，两个萧咪咪，只怕也抵不上他一个。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自从欧阳兄弟死后，你们一直担心找不到人来凑数，现在不现成的就有一个在这里么！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "世上居然有人喜欢挨打，你可瞧见过么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "在下蒋平，却不知各位尊姓大名？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "兄台年纪虽轻，想必也听说过'十大恶人'的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，你瞧见他这张嘴，也该知道他是谁的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "小兄弟你只管放心，咱们来找你，并没有什么恶意。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "各位俱是武林前辈，自然不会找在下这无名后辈麻烦的，在下非但十分放心，而且今日得见武林前辈的风采，更实在高兴得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你们瞧，这孩子多会说话，嘴上就好像抹了蜜似的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，这样的人，连我和尚见了都欢喜，也就难怪树上的这位小姑娘，不惜为他玩命了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "树上那位姑娘，与在下虽然相识，却不过只是道义之交而已，哪里有什么男女之情，前辈说笑了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "既然是道义之交，人家赤条条地被吊在树上，你为什么不去救她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "在下虽有相救之心，怎奈……怎奈男女授受不亲，如今她不幸遭人羞侮赤身露体，在下若是去救她，岂非多有不便。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "如此说来，你倒是个正人君子了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "在下虽然浪迹江湖，但这礼义两字，倒也未敢忘记。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你们瞧，他是不是有两下子，莫说萧咪咪，就连欧阳兄弟见了他，也非得拜他做师父不行。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，欧阳兄弟说话，三句中至少还有一句是真的，但他一共只说了四句半话，却有四句是假的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "前辈又说笑了，在前辈面前，在下怎敢说谎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不敢说谎么？哈哈，这就又是一句谎话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你说的句句都是实话？好，那么我问你，你若是蒋平，有个叫江玉郎的小坏蛋，却又是谁呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "要在前辈们面前说谎，岂非简直好像鲁班门前弄大斧，孔子庙前卖百家姓，但在下却偏偏自不量力，这还不可笑么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "说得好，说得好，哈哈，这马屁实在刚好拍在咱们屁股上，拍得恰到好处，舒服极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "前辈们未和在下说话之前，想必早已将在下的底细都摸清了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，咱们非但早已知道你叫江玉郎，是江南大侠的宝贝儿子，也知道这位小情人本是移花宫的门下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道咱们为什么会对你如此关心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "莫非前辈们想替在下做媒么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我若有女儿，宁可嫁给李大嘴，也不会嫁给你，李大嘴至少还不会吃她的脑袋，但是你，吃了人只怕连骨头都不会吐出来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "前辈过奖了，在下怎比得上李老前辈？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你也用不着客气，我吃人最多只不过是一个个的吃，但你吃人却是一队队的往下吞。'双狮镖局'的那些人，不是被你一夜之间全都吞下去了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "前辈们将在下调查得如此清楚，是为了什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你也许不知道，自从欧阳兄弟两人死了后，'十大恶人'其实剩下九个了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "前辈莫非是想找个人来代替欧阳兄弟的位置？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，咱们若想重振'十大恶人'的名声，非找个生力军不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "但这人倒的确难找得很，据在下所知，江湖中够资格能和前辈并驾齐驱的人，只怕还没有几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "远在天边，近在眼前，你就是一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "在下怎当得起！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，你用不着客气，你年纪轻轻，已有这么样的成就，再过两年，只怕连咱们都没法子和你相比。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "不敢当，不敢当，前辈们如此抬举在下，却叫在下如何报答呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "有意思，有意思，你能说出这句话来，就表示你这人实在够意思得很，也不枉咱们对你另眼相看了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但小伙子你可千万莫上他们的当，他们拉你入伙，只不过是要你为他们做件事而已。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "前辈虽是一番好意，但在下若能有机会为前辈们效劳，正也是不胜荣幸之至，前辈们有何吩咐，只管说出来就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "武林中有个极厉害的人物，叫魏无牙，他就住在这山上，你自然也知道的，但你可知道，他那老鼠洞里现在来了位贵客么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "这世上若只有一个在下不愿打交道的人，那就是魏无牙了。就算天下的人都死尽死绝，在下也不愿和他有任何来往，他洞里是否来了位贵客，在下既不会知道，也绝不想知道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "只可惜这位贵客却偏偏是你认得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "我认得？我怎会认得？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "魏无牙平生没有一个朋友，就连他们'十二星相'中的人，瞧见他都像是见了鬼一样，避之惟恐不及。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "这正是：老鼠过街，人人喊打。愿意和毒蛇猛兽为伍的人，在下倒也见过几个，但愿意和老鼠交朋友的人，只怕连一个都不会有。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你错了，愿意和老鼠交朋友的人，也有一个的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "事实上他简直已将魏无牙哄得服服帖帖，他无论说什么，魏无牙都听他的，魏无牙这辈子从来也没有对别人这么好过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "如此说来，这位仁兄的本事倒的确不小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道这人是谁么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "在下实在想不出有神通如此广大的朋友。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "谁说他是你的朋友……你虽没有神通如此广大的朋友，却有个神通广大的老子，你难道忘了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "是我爹爹？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，魏无牙的贵客，就是江南大侠江别鹤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "想不到家父居然和魏无牙交上了朋友。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "和魏无牙交上朋友又有什么不好，有了这么硬的靠山，就算移花宫主想找他的麻烦，他也用不着害怕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "那么，前辈的意思是要在下做什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你若成了魏无牙的贵客，在那洞中自然就可随意走动……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "前辈莫非是要在下打听件什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错．和你这样有头脑的人说话，的确是件令人愉快的事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那也不是什么大不了的事，只不过，咱们有几只箱子，据说已落在魏无牙手里，你不妨顺便去瞧瞧箱子是不是真的在那里？若在那里，是在什么地方？然后咱们再一起想法子把它弄出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "却不知那是几只什么样的箱子？箱子里装的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，那只不过是几只破铁箱子而已，是黑色的，看起来又笨又重，那么笨重的箱子，别人绝不会有，所以你一看就会知道的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "箱子里本来装着有些珠宝，但魏无牙说不定已将珠宝拿出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "箱子既已是空的，前辈们为何还要苦苦寻找？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "在别人眼中，那虽然只是几口破铁箱子，但在咱们眼中，它却是无价之宝。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "无价之宝？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哈哈，这无价之宝，却是一两银子也卖不出去的，只不过因为箱子上的油漆有些不同，所以在咱们眼中才变得十分珍贵。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道那油漆是用什么调成的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那是用血调成的，是用咱们仇人的血调成的，咱们这些人都已老了，老得连雄心都已消磨，只有那几口箱子，还可以令咱们重想起以前那些光辉灿烂的日子，所以咱们无论如何，也不能让它落在别人手里。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "若是世俗的珍宝，无论有多少，既已落在魏无牙手里，咱们也就算了，犯不上冒险去老虎头上拔毛，咱们就算等着要花钱，到别的地方去抢，岂非容易得多么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但这几口箱子若丢了，咱们这辈子就完蛋大吉，所以，小兄弟你无论如何，也得帮咱们这个忙，咱们一定忘不了你的好处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "小兄弟，你难道不信咱们的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "那几口箱子在别人眼中既是不值一文，魏无牙必然不会看重的，他若已取出箱子里的珍宝，说不定早已将箱子抛却。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "咱们也曾考虑过这问题，所以魏无牙若已将箱子抛却，就烦小兄弟你打听打听，他将箱子抛到什么地方去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "咱们现在虽已是自己人，但也不会要小兄弟你白辛苦的，只要事成，咱们一定想法子去弄万两黄金，和几个妖娇百媚的美人儿来让你享受享受，而且还保证替你保守所有的秘密。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "前辈可要在下立刻就去么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "自然是越快越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "那么她……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但现在你总该已知道，你和她缠在一起，是只有麻烦，没有好处的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "就算有好处，也不会有麻烦多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "正是如此，何况，她长得虽不差，身材也不错，但只要你事成之后，我负责替你找十个比她更迷人的小姑娘来。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "而且我还可以先教给她们几手，可以让你欲仙欲死的功夫。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "既是如此，在下立刻就走，只不过，在下事成之后，该如何和前辈们联络呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "无论事成不成，三天之后，你到洞口兜个圈子，咱们自然会想法子和你说话的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "好，就是这样，一言为定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子走得那么快，我看有些不保险。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，他这是怕移花宫主来找他算帐的，所以赶紧想躲到那老鼠洞里去。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看他对咱们说的话，未必就真的相信了，你们若认为他真的会为你们找箱子，那才是做梦。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "我说的话既合情，又合理，他为什么不信？何况，这小子又贪财，又好色，万两黄金、十个大美人儿难道还打不动他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他就算找着箱子，未必会交给你们的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "他不交给咱们，要那几口空箱子又有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这小子是个聪明人，只要用几口空箱子来换黄金美人，这么划算的事他难道还会不做？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但换过来之后，我一定要告诉他这几口又旧又破的空箱子，究竟有什么好处，我们要瞧瞧他那时的脸色。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "哈哈，那时他脸色一定比你的屁股还要难看得多。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "喂！小姑娘，上面的风很大，你不怕着凉么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你这小子背上还背着一个，又想打别人的主意了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "这位小姑娘孤苦伶仃，又偏偏遇着个没有心肝的薄情郎，实在怪可怜的，我不去安慰她谁去安慰她。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "很好，你快去安慰她吧！但等到移花宫主找上门来时，你可莫怪咱们不帮你的忙了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "老实说，像她这么样痛苦的人，我也安慰不了的，何况，我袋子里已有了一个，年纪虽然大些，但姜是老的辣，老的才去火。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你现在总算懂得些男女之间的门道了，只可惜男人却是年轻力壮的才好，否则我……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "幸好我年纪大些，否则若被你看上，那才真是天大的麻烦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 96,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    }
